          Talents héroiques&nbsp;<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-collapse-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </a>
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div id="heroic" class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="h_heroic">
